<h2 class="bold font-l">The Real & Fake Intertwine</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The Mane 6 start to get separated and start encountering their mean clones in separate situations, mistaking the clones for their actual friends. In this case, Mean Twilight learns the location of the Tree of Harmony from Mane Pinkie, and Mane Fluttershy briefly witnesses Mean Rainbow. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="w1ii1n" data-video-descrip="Mistaken identities abound when the Mean 6 meet the real ponies in different spots, which could ruin their camping retreat." data-video-title="The Real &amp; Fake Intertwine (2)" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/w1ii1n_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://mediaproxy.tvtropes.org/width/250/https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/images/vlcsnap_2021_01_07_12h31m31s431.png" data-video-trope="Main/Farce" data-video-tropename="Farce" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/MyLittlePonyFriendshipIsMagic" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://mediaproxy.tvtropes.org/width/250/https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/images/vlcsnap_2021_01_07_12h31m31s431.png">
<p><span class="bold">The Real & Fake...</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="1wbwk3" data-video-descrip="Mistaken identities between real and fake continue; this such misunderstanding causes a heated argument between the real Twilight and the real Pinkie." data-video-title="The Real &amp; Fake Intertwine (3)" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/1wbwk3_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://mediaproxy.tvtropes.org/width/250/https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/images/vlcsnap_2021_01_07_12h32m07s072.png" data-video-trope="Main/Farce" data-video-tropename="Farce" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/MyLittlePonyFriendshipIsMagic" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://mediaproxy.tvtropes.org/width/250/https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/images/vlcsnap_2021_01_07_12h32m07s072.png">
